Isantya esipheleleyo somgangatho wemveliso ye-veneer sisetyenziselwa iidayimitha ezahlukeneyo zokuxhuba iinkuni kunye nokusebenza okunxulumene noko. Kufuneka kuphela umntu omnye oza kusebenza. Igcina iindleko zomsebenzi ezingaphezulu. Kwangelo xesha, akukho ukuyeka ukuvelisa, ke imveliso inyuke kakhulu. Ngapha koko, inqanaba lesiphoso liphantsi kakhulu.
1.The ngokupheleleyo oluzenzekelayo log ukusika isarha -Ukusika iinkuni ubungakanani enkulu ibe 4ft okanye 8ft okanye ezinye ubukhulu ezifunekay
... 
nye ye-debarke kunye neeroller ezimbini zohlobo lwe-mace olwenza ukuba kube lula ukubamba iinkuni kunye nokuphakamisa ukusebenza ngokufanelekileyo. Sineemodeli ezimbini: 1. umfuziselo otyumkileyo onokuthi utyumle inkunkuma efakiweyo ukuze kube lula ukuthuthwa nokusetyenziswa. 2.imodeli eqhelekileyo ngaphandle kokutyunyuzwa
3. Umlayishi welog - oku kuyangqinelana nomatshini oxobukayo. Ukusebenza okuzenzekelayo ngomatshini wokuxobuka. Akukho sidingo sokuba abantu basebenze. Gcina iindleko zabasebe
...
 be-veneer kunye nobukhulu buchaneke ngakumbi. Isantya umsebenzi ohlengahlengiswayo kunye nobunzima kunye nokuvalwa kokuntywila kwenaliti kunye nesikwere isikhokelo sesiporo somgaqo kwenza umatshini womelele kwaye uzinze kwaye unganxibi kakhulu.
Isitaki se-Veneer -I-stacker inokulinganisa ngokuzenzekelayo isantya somatshini wokuxobuka, iimveliso ezingafanelekanga zinokucwangciswa ngokuzenzekelayo ngokweemfuno.Imisebenzi efana nokubala okuzenzekelayo kunye nokuothusa, ukuhambisa ngokuzenzekelayo.

Imigca yokupakisha ihlelwa ngokweempawu zokusabela kwenkqubo.
Ukupakishwa komgca wendibano eqhubekayo inkqubo yokulawula.
Iiparamitha kwinkqubo yokutshintsha ziyaqhubeka, oko kukuthi, ukuhanjiswa komqondiso wenkqubo kunye nokuphendula kwento elawulwayo yimali eqhubekayo engaphazamisekiyo okanye ubuninzi be-analog.Ulawulo lobushushu olukhankanywe ngaphambili, iinkqubo zokulawula isantya semoto ziinkqubo eziqhubekayo zokulawula.Ngokobudlelwane phakathi kobuninzi bemveliso kunye nobungakanani begal
... 
ula kwaye ngoko ke ulawulo oluphunyeziweyo yinkqubo luyimfuneko.Iisistim eziqhelekileyo zokulawula i-relay contactor, iinkqubo zokulawula ezicwangcisiweyo, njl. zitshintsha iinkqubo zokulawula.Kukho iintlobo ezimbini zeenkqubo zokulawula ukutshintshwa: i-open-loop kunye ne-closed-loop.Ithiyori yolawulo lokutshintsha iluphu evulekileyo isekwe kwi-algebra enengqondo.
Ngokunyuka kwe-automation yemigca yendibano yokupakisha, ukusebenza, ukugcinwa kunye nokugcinwa kwesiqhelo koomatshini bokupakisha k
...
kelayo kunye nomgca wokuhlanganisa ulula, ubeka iimfuno eziphezulu ekusebenzeni okuguquguqukayo kokuhanjiswa, okudinga ukusebenza ngokukhawuleza kokulandelela okuguquguqukayo kunye nokuchaneka kwesantya esiphezulu esizinzile.Ngoko ke kuyimfuneko ukuqwalasela iinkcukacha eziguquguqukayo zomguquli we-frequency kunye nokukhetha ukusebenza okuphezulu, okuguquguqukayo kunye nomgangatho ophezulu wokuguqulela ukuhlangabezana neemfuno zomgca wokupakisha wemveliso oqhubekayo.

Ngu Bathandwa Ndlangisa
Usomashishini uTshego Mathe uzokwenza imbali okokuqala ngokuphehlelela ukhuphiswano loonobuhle, oluzakuvuleleka kumanina anolwazi lomtshato kuphela.
Olukhuphiswano luvuleleke kubantu abatshatileyo, asele bohlukene nabalingani ebebetshate nabo kunye nabahlolokazi baseSoweto kuphela.
Injongo yolukhuphiswano kukuxhobisa amanina, nokubhiyozela izakhono zawo ezohlukeneyo, kwaye uMrs Soweto uzakujongana ngqo nokulwa imicelimingeni eyimiqobo kwimpilo yamanina kunye namabala abek
... 
eneyo kunye nemilinganiselo eyohlukileyo. Sifuna ukuqubisana neenkolelo eziqingqiweyo ngobuhle, azibona enyanzelekile amanina ukuba makazilandele kwaye sibhiyozele ubuntu babo ngokwahlukeneyo,” utshilo uMathe.
UMathe unethemba lokuba olukhuphiswano aluzuveza elibala izakhono zabagqatswa kuphela, kodwa luzakuza nophuhliso olubonakalayo kwindawo abahlala kuzo.
“Into endifuna ukuyibona luphuhliso oluzakwenzeka kwingingqi abahlala kuzo abagqatswa kunye nabazikhethileyo,” utshilo.
Unethemba lokubamba
...
le nezifundo zabo okanye ukuqala amashihsini abo. Sikholelwa ukuba ngokuxhobisa amanina, sixhobisa ingqingqi iphelele.”
Ukhuphiswano luka Mrs Soweto kulindeleke ukuba luphehlelwe ngoMgqibelo umhla wesine kweyoKwindla, kwindawo i-Ubuntu Kraal.
Ngokuka Mathe, ukuphehlelwa kuka Mrs Soweto akukho malunga nokubhiyozela amanina aseSoweto kuphela, kodwa kukubonakalisa amandla oluntu lwasekuhlaleni nokubaluleka kokuxhobisa amanina kwilizwe loMzantsi Afrika liphela.
Umfanekiso ongasentla: NguTshego Mate.

ima bomrhumo.
Ukongeza kuyilo kunye nophuhliso lweemachinese ezizodwa ukunciphisa iindleko, ukusetyenziswa kweentlobo ezahlukeneyo zomatshini wokulungisa i-CNC ukuqinisekisa ukuchaneka, kodwa nokusetyenziswa kweJamani, iJapan kunye namanye amazwe ahambele phambili ukwenza uninzi lweziprofeto zokugaya ukhuko lolona luphucukileyo ukwenza.
Inkqubo yolawulo yenkqubo, ukunciphisa impazamo yomntu, ukuphunyezwa kolawulo lomgangatho olubanzi, ukuze inkqubo nganye ibe nomgangatho wokulawula umzi mveliso.

Y2Uthotho lweenjini zombane ophezulu zivalwe ngokupheleleyounomatse-ekhejiniiinjini.Iinjini zenziwa ngeklasi yokukhuselaIP54, indlela yokupholisaI-IC411,iklasi ye-insulation F, kunye nelungiselelo lokuxhomaIMB3.Umbane olinganisiweyo yi-6kv okanye i-10KV.
Olu chungechunge lweenjini zenzelwe ngesakhelo sentsimbi ephosiweyo, enobungakanani obuncinci kunye nesakhiwo esincinci.Iinjini zineempawu ezilungileyo zokusebenza okuphezulu, ingxolo ephantsi, ukungcangcazela okuphantsi, ukusebenza okuthembekileyo, ukufakwa lula kunye nokugcinwa.Isetyenziswa ngokubanzi ukuqhuba oomatshini abahlukeneyo, njengecompressor, i-ventilator, impompo, kunye ne-crusher.Iimotor zisenokusetyenziswa njengeyona nto iphambili kwi-petrochemical, amayeza, amasimi emigodi nakwiimeko ezirhabaxa zokusingqongileyo.

di esizifumanayo zikwiifomathi ezahlukeneyo kubandakanya iPDF ke ziyafundeka phantse kuso nasiphi na isixhobo. Injini yokukhangela enamandla isenza sikwazi ukufumana nasiphi na isihloko ngombhali okanye ngesihloko ngexesha elifutshane kakhulu.

Ngaba unegumbi lokuhlambela elincinci okanye elinesityalo esinzima? Akukho nanye kwiibhafu ozifumanayo emarikeni ekuqinisekisayo? Ezi zizathu akufanele zenze ukuba ulahle ukuba nebhafu kwindawo yokuhlambela. Iibhafu ezakhelwe ngaphakathi Zisisisombululo esihle esingayi kukuvumela kuphela ukuba wenze uninzi lwendawo, kodwa kwaye uzenzele ukuba ulungele wena.
Ukukhetha ibhafu eyakhelwe-ngaphakathi yenye yeendlela ezininzi esinazo zokubonelela igumbi lokuhlambela ngesithuba esifanelekileyo sokuhlam
... 
, ngaloo ndlela ufezekisa indawo yanamhlanje kunye necocekileyo njenge-spa.
Ukuze ezi zibonelelo zingafiphazwa kwixesha elizayo ngenxa yeengxaki zokufuma okanye ukuvuza, kuya kufuneka phathisa ingcali ukuze iphunyezwe. Ukungangeni kwamanzi okufanelekileyo kubalulekile ukubathintela, ngoko ke buza kwaye u-odole umsebenzi kwinkampani okanye kwingcali eneembekiselo.
Izinto zokuhlambela zangoku
Imarble, i-ceramics, i-microcement, ikhonkrithi epholisiweyo, iipeyinti zobugcisa ezinokumelana okuphezulu
...
iso esikhuthazayo namhlanje ifumane obu buhle buncinci kunye nobucocekileyo obubanika isambatho esikhethekileyo. Ubuhle obukumema ukuba uphumle kwaye asiyiyo le nto siyifunayo xa sihlamba?
Ngokuqinisekileyo ayinguye wonke umntu othanda le ndlela kwaye uzimisele ukuyilungelelanisa. Ukuba unaloo mbono, ungabheja usebenzisa i-coating efanayo kwibhafu eyakhelwe-ngaphakathi kunye nodonga okanye umgangatho, ukubheja kwezinye izinto ze-ceramic okanye ukhuni ukwenza umahluko.

Xa kudityaniswe izixhobo yezihlangu kuphela ngoku, ndayomisa ngeentende kabini iye isisombululo kakhulu lula engcono. Ukhuseleko onyawo kuyafikelelwa yi banxibe bokuxhathisa kwaye anti-slip komsebenzi outsole, nto leyo iqaphelwa ekukhanyeni athambileyo iimpawu midsole. Intuthuzelo xa ehamba.
Ukusuka lo mbono, eyona indibaniselwano yangoku UR / DB, esebenzisa irabha (UR) ukwenza outsole, lyu (DB) njengoko midsole, uze emva koko ngokusebenzisa iglu okanye imichiza nisondelelane umsebenzi kunye umsebenzi lib DB ngokwayo iibhondi i outsole ukuya midsole. Kakade ke, ndayomisa ngeentende kumphandle isihlangu kwakhona likhazimliswe, olubengezelayo, kwaye eqingqiweyo.
Kukho kwakhona indibanisela eziphathekayo kuphela, ezizezi DB / AKA (lyu / lyu thermoplastic). Kuyinto ukhululekile ukuba ukunxiba. Ngaphezu koko, ukusetyenziswa lyu thermoplastic ukwenza outsole idibana neemfuno abayili wanamhla, kuba nakuphumla intende eyenziwe AKA inokuvelisa kuphela enemibala, kwaye inkqubo nangokukrola kwi yintende nako zinokohluka.
Enye kuphela kabini-umaleko eyenziwe DB / DB (lyu / lyu) izinto ngaxeshanye, outsole kunye midsole enziwe lyu. Kuba outsole, kukho izinto lyu ingakumbi ashinyeneyo kufuneka isetyenziswe ukulondoloza iimpawu banxibe kweelana le outsole. Kuba midsole, lyu foamed kufuneka sikhetwe intuthuzelo.

Adil igama elona lifanelekileyo: Namhlanje, Esebenzayo, Ujonge, I-temperamental, Ufanele. Fumana Adil intsingiselo yegama.
Chaudhary intsingiselo egqibeleleyo yegama: Ufanele, Esebenzayo, Inhlanhla, Bokudala, I-temperamental. Fumana Chaudhary intsingiselo yesinti.
Adil imvelaphi yegama lokuqala. Turkish form of Adil. Fumana Adil imvelaphi yegama lokuqala.
Chaudhary umvelaphi. From a title meaning "holder of four", from Sanskrit चतुर् (chatur) meaning "four" and धुरीय (dhuriya) "bearing a burden". Fumana Chaudhary umvelaphi.
Igama lokugqibela Chaudhary eliqhelekileyo Fiji, Indiya, Lawos. Fumana Chaudhary ifani isasazeka.
Amagama alinganayo for Adil kumazwe ahlukeneyo neelwimi: Adel, Adil. Fumana Adil kwezinye iilwimi.
Amagama angamafanel 'Chaudhary kumazwe ahlukeneyo neelwimi: Chaudhuri, Choudhury, Chowdhury. Fumana Chaudhary kwezinye iilwimi.
Amagama amaninzi aqhelekileyo ngegama Adil: Guleria, Shamim, Mirza, Mohammed, Shah. Fumana Uluhlu lwamagama egama Adil.
Amagama aqhelekileyo ngegama lokugqibela Chaudhary: Latashiya, Sachin, Namita, Sahil, Visuja. Fumana Amagama ahamba kunye Chaudhary.
Ukuhambisana Adil kunye Chaudhary yi 81%. Fumana Ukuhambelana Adil kunye Chaudhary.

Ngomhla wesithandathu ngenyanga yeSilimela ngonyaka ka1960 amadoda nabafazi baseNgquza baphuma ngamabhunguza neentonga bebonakalisa ukuchasa kwabo iinkqubo zorhulumente wocalucalulo.
Kumongo wengqumbo yamaMpondo yayikukuchasa ukusetyenziswa kwamapasi. Ukwenza oku bayokuhlangana kwintaba yaseNgquza. Amapolisa orhu
... 
e yimpumelelo,” utshilo uMeth.
La madoda adutyulwa ebambe intlanganiso yabahlali eyayizakuthatha isigqibo malunga nokuchasa kwawo ukusekwa korhulumente kazimelegeqe waseTranskie. “La madoda ayechase ukumiliselwa korhulumente wephandle laseTranskei, kunye nenkqubo yamapasi eyayixakile ngalo minyaka,” ucacise watsho uMeth.
Oku kwakulandela emva koqhankqalazo lamakhosikazi olalusinge komkhulu ePitoli ngonyaka ka- 1956, nalapho babechasa inkqubo yokusetyenziswa kwamapasi. Ingxelo ithi ngethuba enyuk
...
a umbuso. Igazi lala madoda lagabula izigcawu nanjengoko ngonyaka olandela lowo kwathi kwasekwa ibutho lomkhosi weANC uMkhonto Wesizwe (16 Disemba 1961).
Urhulumente wentando yesininzi wathiya umasipala wale ndawo ngegama lale ntaba ngelizama ukunika imbeko kuloo maqhawe aseNgquza. “Kunyaka ophelileyo sifake imali ephaya kumakhulu amabini amawaka eerandi, kulo nyaka sijonge ukufaka imali engaphezulu koko kuba sijonge ukusikhulisa esi sikhumbuzo,” utsho uMeth.

a ngo-2015, kodwa ngoku kubonakala ngathi bayifumene. Yifowuni esongelayo necacileyo ngokupheleleyo. Asazi ngokwenyani ukuba luncedo okanye ukusebenza kwesi sixhobo se LG. Nangona ibonakalisiwe njengengcamango enomdla kunye nokuyila.

Esi simemelelo sikaMabuyane siza emva kwesibhengezo sikaMongameli Cyril Ramaphosa ngokuhlwa kwangoLwesine apho adize ukuba kuza kuqhutywa uphando ngakumaqumrhu karhulumente afunyenwe enesandla ekusetyenzisweni gwenxa kwemali egameni leCovid-19.
URamaphosa uthi olu phando luza kwenziwa liButho eliKhethekileyo loPhando, elaziwa njengeSIU. Ukwadize namanye amaqumrhu aquka iNPA, SARS, Hawks, FIC, esithi aza kuqhogelana kuqhutywe uphando.
“Sasiyixelile kwantlandlolo eyokuba akafuneki kubekho buqhophololo xa kusetyenziswa imali ehlelelwe ukusabela kwintsholongwane yeKhorona.
“Njengalo naluphi na ulwaphulomthetho, ubuqhophololo bubeka ubomi (babantu) emngciphekweni,” utshilo uRamaphosa, ekwathi zimalunga namashumi amathathu anesithandathu izehlo zorhwaphilizo eziphandwayo malunga nokusetyenziswa gwenxa kwemali ngexesha leCovid-19.
URamaphosa uthi uza kumane efumana ingxelo yokuba luqhuba njani uphando rhoqo ngeeveki ezintandathu.
Isithethi sikaMabuyane, uMvusiwekhaya Sicwetsha uthe: “INkulubaphathisw’ uMabuyane umemelela kubantu baseMpuma Koloni abanolwazi ngezehlo ezigwenxa nobuqhophololo ukuba basebenzise eli thuba babike kwiSIU ukuze abo babandakanyekayo batshutshiswe.”
INKULUBAPHATHISWA uOscar Mabuyane umemelele kubantu baseMpuma Koloni abanolwazi ngokubiwa nangokudyarhazwa kwemali egameni leCovid-19 ukuba babike kwabasemagunyeni ukuze kuqutyiswane nababandakanyekayo.

IMagshape sisixhobo esisebenzayo semilo kunye nesixhobo sokwakha imisipha. Kufanelekile ukuba unciphise umzimba, ubumbe, ufumane izihlunu, uchithe amanqatha, usebenzise imithambo yevesti kwaye uphakamise inyonga, ilungele impilo.
Kusebenza ngokukodwa kwiimpundu kunye nesisu. Isebenzisa itekhnoloji yentsimi ye-elektroniki egxile kakhulu (HIFEM) ukwenza ityhubhu yexesha elincinci yokuqina kwemisipha, kukhokelela
ukwanda koxinano lwemisipha, ukunciphisa ivolumu, ukucaca okuphuculweyo kunye nokuphucula ithoni.
Yiyo kuphela indlela yokunceda abasetyhini kunye namadoda ukuba bakhe izihlunu kwaye batshise amanqatha, kwaye yeyona ndlela yokuqala engangenisi moya yokunyusa isinqe.

Ukusetyenziswa kwenqanawa kunye nonxweme kunye nenqanawa kunye nenqanawa phakathi kokulayishwa kunye nokukhulula imisebenzi, ekusetyenzisweni kwenkqubo yobunzima besixhobo ngokwayo ilula, kwaye ithatha indawo encinci, isixhobo kwinkqubo yokusebenza. ukusetyenziswa kwayo ngokufanelekileyo kuphezulu kakhulu, kwinkqubo yokusebenza, ukusebenza kwezixhobo kuguquguquka ngakumbi kunye nokusebenza kwezixhobo xa ukusebenza kozinzo kulungile.
Ngokubanzi, ukusetyenziswa okubanzi ngakumbi kweekhreyini zaselwandle kukusetyenziswa kwemisebenzi yothutho lwaselwandle, ngakumbi ekusebenzeni kwempahla yenqanawa kunye nokusebenza kwamanzi emanzini, kunye nokubuyiselwa kunye neminye imisebenzi ebaluleke ngakumbi, enyanisweni, iikhreyini zaselwandle kwi-shipboard. imisebenzi kunemisebenzi yomhlaba iimfuno ezingqongqo ngakumbi, nto leyo ebangelwa ulwandle hayi kuphela ukuhambisa iimpahla, kodwa ngokutsho ezinye intsebenzo ekhethekileyo ukuze inqanawa yokulawula.

Oku kuyimpembelelo engqongqo yokuba Purva Chaudhary inabantu. Ngamanye amazwi, oku kukuthi abantu bayazi ngokungaqondi xa beva eli gama kunye neenfani. Ngeempawu eziphawulwe kakhulu, intsingiselo yeengqondo ezingapheliyo yegama inamandla. Oku kukubona okungenakuqonda kwabantu abaninzi xa beva eli gama. Yikhumbule ukuba okuphawulekayo kukuphawulekayo - ukubaluleka kwengqondo nokungazi kakuhle kwegama kunamandla.
Yintoni Purva Chaudhary ithetha ukuthini
Iingcaciso eziphambili ze Purva Chaudhary. Yabelana ngalesi sithombe kubahlobo.

Democrat-Gazette yi-paywall ecaleni kwiphepha lewebhu. Yayibekwa emva koko ngo-2002 xa amaninzi amanye amaphepha ayengaphantsi kweengcamango ukuba ukuba benze iiwebhusayithi zabo zikhululekileyo, ingeniso evela kwi-intengiso ye-intanethi yayiza kuba yiphubi legolide ekupheleni komnkantsha (sonke sibonile ukuba phandle.)
I-Democrat-Gazette ine-3,500 ababhalisile kuphela kwi-intanethi, kungekhona inani elikhulu kwiphepha elinokupapashwa kweeveki ze-170,000 (ngeSonto 270,000).
Kodwa ababhalisile ba
...
manqaku angama-20 ngenyanga kwaye bahlawule emva koko. Iziphumo kude kube ngoku zikhuthaza. I-Traffic kwiwebhusayithi yephepha yanda nangemva kokuba i-paywall yenziwe.
Ngoko masiqokelele: Esikhundleni sokutshitshisa i-newsprint nokunikela umxholo we-intanethi, ifomula yokufumana inzuzo ibonakala iphendulela: Qhubeka uprinta iphephancwadi uze uhlawule iwebhusayithi.
Kutheni oko kukuchasene ngqo noko kuthethwa yi-media media pundits. Ngaba ngaba ngaba ngaba ngaba ngabaprofeti (gulp) bangalunganga?

Itshantliziyo lamalungelo abasebenzi uVusi Mahlangu uthi, useza kuqhubeka esilwela abasebenzi beYunivesithi iWalter Sisulu nangona ebebanjwe wavalelwa kwiveki ezimbini ezidlulileyo ngezityholo zokuphosisa nokulahlekisa ingalo yomthetho.
UMahlangu ukutsho oku ngethuba ethetha nabasebenzi abalinganiselwa kumakhulu amathathu eFreedom Square eMthatha ngoLwesihlanu, kwimizuzwana nje ekhululwe yinkundla yamatyala ngebheyile yamakhulu amathandathu eerandi (R600).
“Sizoliphumelela eli dabi, andizukurhoxa kuba ndiphuma ejele. Ukubanjwa kwam kundenze ndanamandla ndakhuthazeka nangakumbi, ndibulela inkxaso endiyifumeneyo kubasebenzi. Lo nto ibonakalise ukuba eli dabi alikho ngam kodwa ngabasebenzi bonke,” utshilo uMahlangu, ongumfundi e-Unisa.
Umemelele abasebenzi bezinye iiyunivesithi ukuba bangenelele balwele amalungelo abo. Bebonke abasebenzi abebezonika inkxaso enkundleni balinganiselwa kumakhulu amathathu.
Umbuso awukhange ukuchase ukunikwa kwebheyile uMahlangu. Igqwetha lakhe uBayethe Maswazi lithi, isamangalisa into yokubanjwa kwakhe ngamapolisa emveni kokuxhwilwa.
Ukwathi okwangoku akanawutsho umbuso unetyala eliluqilima ngakumrhanelwa.
UVuyo Mtonintshi wephulo #OutsourcingMustFall eWSU, uthi ababuyi ngamva kwaye abasebenzi abanangxaki nakugxothwa, kodwa elidabi bazoliphumelela. Inkundla ilimisele umhla weshumi elinanye kweyeKhala kulo nyaka ityala.

...
ali semali-mboleko oyifunayo, gcwalisa isicelo esifutshane se-intanethi, usithumele, kwaye ulinde unikezelo.

Ngaphandle kwentshukumo eqhubekekayo ebhekisa kubuchwephesha bokunyuka komhlaba (i-SMT) kunye nobunzima obandayo, indibano ye "Through-Hole" isenendima enkulu ekufuneka iyidlalile, eneneni nakwiindibano eziphambili zomphezulu wentaba kuhlala kukho into ethile yemingxunya efunekayo. Ngamava angaphezu kwe-50 anamava e-IPC-A-610 yabasebenzi abaqeqeshiweyo kwindibano yesandla kunye nokuthengiswa kwesandla ngesandla, siyakwazi ukubonelela ngemveliso ekumgangatho ophezulu ngokuhambelana nexesha elifanelekileyo.
Zombini zikhokelwa kwaye zikhokele ukuthengisa simahla ngaphandle kokucoceka, isinyibilikisi, iinkqubo ze-ultrasonic kunye nezamanzi zokucoca ezikhoyo. Ukongeza ekuboneleleni ngazo zonke iintlobo zebandla elinomngxunya, ukutyabeka okuguqulweyo kunokufumaneka ukugqitywa kwemveliso.
Ngokubanzi, sinikezela ngenkonzo ye-THT:

badlali. Emdlalweni ogqithileyo sibethwe nje ziimpazamo ezincinci nobumanzi bebala – kodwa siza kuzama ukulwa kule veki,” utshilo uMngwevu. Yonke imidlalo iza kuqala ngentsimbi yesithathu ngoMgqibelo.

Umahluko oPhambili – Izongezo vs Imixube
Izongezo kunye ne-admixtures zizinto zekhemikhali ezongezwa kwezinye izinto ukuphucula iikhemikhali zazo kunye neempawu zomzimba.Nangona zombini ziyinxalenye yongezwa kwezinye izinto, kukho umahluko phakathi kwezongezo kunye ne-admixtures xa kufikwa kwimixube yesamente kunye nekhonkrithi.Izongezo zinokuba zizongezo zokutya okanye nayiphi na enye into edityaniswe kwinto ngomlinganiselo omncinci ukuyiphucula okanye ukuyigcina.I-Admixtures, ngakolunye uhlang
... 
ka kwisamente ukuya kulwakhiwo.
Ezinye ii-accelerators ezifakwe kwisamente yi-calcium chloride (CaCl2), i-sodium chloride (NaCl), amanzi olwandle kunye ne-potassium chloride (KCl).
Yintoni iAdmixtures
I-Admixtures zizinto zekhemikhali ezongezwa kwimixube yekhonkrithi ngelixa zixutywa ukufumana iipropati ezintsha.Imixube ngamalungu ekhonkrithi ngaphandle kwesamente, amanzi kunye neeaggregates.I-Admixtures yongezwa kwi-samente ngokukhawuleza ngaphambi okanye ngexesha lokuxuba umxube wekhonkrithi.

...
xtures yokugcina umoya, i-plasticizers, i-admixtures yokunciphisa amanzi, njl.
Ukuqukumbela
Izongezo zongezwa kwisamente ngelixa kuveliswa.I-Admixtures yongezwa kumxube wekhonkrithi ngaphambi okanye ngexesha lokuxuba.Umahluko ophambili phakathi kwezongezo kunye ne-admixtures kukuba izongezo zongezwa kwisamente ngexesha lokuvelisa ukufumana iipropathi ezintsha zesamente ngelixa i-admixtures yongezwa kwimixube yekhonkrithi ngelixa ixutywa ukufumana iipropathi ezintsha.

Uyilo Lwewebhu Kwaye Ux I-Sí, Me Quiero iwebhusayithi yindawo enceda ukuba ube ngokwakho. Ukuqhuba iprojekthi, udliwanondlebe kufuneka lwenziwe kunye nemeko yezentlalo nenkcubeko ngokunxulumene nabasetyhini kwafuneka iphononongwe; ingqokelela yakhe eluntwini kunye naye. Kwagqitywa kwelokuba iwebhusayithi iya kuba yinto yokudibana kwaye iya kuqhutywa ngendlela yokunceda ekuzithandeni ngokwakho. Uyilo lubonakaliswa ngokulula kunye neethoni ezingathathi hlangothi zisebenzisa umahluko obomvu ukutsala ingqalelo kwizenzo ezithile, imibala yophawu lwencwadi olupapashwe ngumthengi. Ukuphefumlelwa kwavela kubugcisa bokuzoba.
Igama leprojekthi : Si Me Quiero, Igama labayili : Ana Ramirez, Igama lomthengi : Little Red studio.
Olu luyilo olumangalisayo luphumelele imbasa yoyilo lwesilivere kwifashoni, isinxibo kunye nokhuphiswano loyilo lwesambatho. Ngokuqinisekileyo kuya kufuneka ubone iipotifoliyo yoyilo lwesilivere esiphumelele ukufumana ezinye izinto ezintsha, ezintsha, ezendalo kunye nefashoni yoyilo, iimpahla kunye noyilo lwempahla.

EKapa – Umbutho wabafundi oyinxalenye ye Economic Freedom Fighters unkqenkqeza phambili kunyulo lwebhunga labafundi kwiikhampasi ezimbini zaseCPUT.
Iziphumo zekhampasi iMowbray zibonakalisa ukuba abagqatswa beliqela baziphumelele zonke izihlalo. Zife namthanyana inzame ze South African Students Congress (SASCO) kunye ne Pan African Students Movement of Azania (PASMA) zokuqubisana ne EFFSC.
Kananjalo nakwikhampasi iBellville, ibethe ngesinye, yatsho igqugqisa zonke izihlalo ebiqubisana ngazo kunye nePASMA neSASCO.
Zixubile noko iziphumo zaseWellington nalapho abagqatswa abazimeleyo befumene izihlalo ezimbalwa, yaze iSASCO yafumana esinye. Akukacaci ke ukuba kugqityiwe kusini na ukubalwa ngoba kwizihlalo ezimbalwa kubonakalo kungekho bantu bavotileyo.
Azikaphumi iziphumo zonyulo lwaseDistrict Six emva kokumiswa kobalo ngoLwesihlanu emva kwezikhalazo ezafakwa zinkokheli zabafundi.
Nanjengoba ledyunivesithi inekhampasi ezintlanu, iziphumo zeekhampasi ngeekhampasi zizakudityaniswa kusekwe ibhunga labafundi elizakuquka igcuntswana labo baphumeleleyo abasukwa kwezikhampasi zahlukileyo.
Akukacaci ke ukuba zizakuphuma nini iziphumo zonyulo lwaseDistrict 6. Iinkokheli zabafundi zisixelele ukuba umphathi wenkampani elawula unyulo uzibeke phantsi intambo ekutsheni kwaleveki, isizathu soku asikaziwa. Inzame zokuqhagamshelana nabaphathi balenkampani khange ziphumelele xeshana sipapasha elinqaku.

...

IHebei Guanlang Biotechnology Co., Ltd. yenye yezona ziphambili abathengisi beprocaine eTshayina, sivelisa procaine ukusuka kumzi-mveliso wethu kunye neteknoloji yethu ikakhulu kubathengi abavela eYurophu naseMelika.
Procaine Basic Info.
I-CAS: 59-46-1
MF: C13H20N2O2
MW: 236.31
I-EINECS: 200-426-9
Iimpawu zeMichiza : ikristale emhlophe.
Ukusetyenziswa kwe-inhibitor ye-sodium channel. Ii-anesthetics zasekhaya.
Isiphumo setyhefu sokuthobeka, ngokukhawuleza kwaye sikhuselekile. Ifanelekile kwi-anesthesia yendawo, isetyenziswe kwiso, indlebe, impumlo, amazinyo, ukusebenza, isetyenziselwa i-anesthesia yokungena, i-anesthesia kunye nomphathi wonyango oluvaliweyo. Imveliso ikwasetyenziswa kwimveliso yeprocaine ipenicillin.
IHebei Guanlang Biotechnology Co., Ltd. yeyeQela laseGuanlang, elasekwa ngo-2007, elikwidolophu yaseShijiazhuang eyinkunzi yePhondo leHebei kunye necandelo le-hub phakathi kweBeijing Tianjin kunye neHebei kwaye inenzuzo yokuhamba ngokulula. Inkampani yethu lishishini lemichiza lanamhlanje elinobuchwepheshe obuphezulu kunye noPhando noPhuhliso, imveliso kunye nokuthengisa.

... 
ngxaki, iqela lokwakha lihlala lisebenzisa i-insulators. Nangona kunjalo, kwimigca yokuhambisa amandla ombane aphezulu, i-pin okanye i-disc insulator imitya iyafuneka ukuba idityaniswe kwingalo yomnqamlezo kwicala elithe tyaba. ngi. Nokuba kukhetho lwezinto, ubugcisa, ulawulo lomgangatho okanye inkonzo yasemva kwentengiso, sizabalazela ukugqwesa. Injongo yethu kukubonelela abathengi ngeseti yesisombululo esisebenza ngokulula, esilula nesifanelekileyo somnyango.

Umbuzo: Ndingaba kanjani ngumhambisi wakho ekuphela kwemarike?

Iqela lolawulo lezixhobo ezikhuselweyo kwezoqoqosho kunye namagosa emicimbi yezasekhaya aye athontelana kwindlu eseKraaifontein ngoLwesithathu.
Isithethi sooKhetshe uW/O Zinzi Hani uthi oku kubanjwa kulandela ukubhaqwa kwexhoba ebelithutyeleziswa lisuka eNigeria ebutsheni balo nyaka.
“Ukubanjwa kwakhe kuphuma kuphando olwaqala ekuqaleni kwalo nyaka, nalapho kwafunyaniswa ukuba umrhanelwa warhweba ixhoba eNigeria ngenjongo zokuxhaphaza ngokwesondo,” utshilo uHani.
“Uphando lwangaphambili kunye nodliwano-ndlebe olwenziwa ngoonontlalontle bafumanise ukuba amaxhoba amane anokuba ngamaxhoba okurhweba ngabantu ngokungekho mthethweni kodwa akukho mthethweni eMzantsi Afrika.” UZinzi uthi aba bane babanjwe babekwa ityala lokwaphula umthetho i-Immigration Act.
Umtyholwa ngokuba ngumrhwebi, uzakuvela kwinkundla kamantyi eKuilsriver ngoLwesihlanu ngezityholo zokurhweba ngabantu ngokungekho mthethweni kunye nokwaphula umthetho iImmigration Act.

Ngaba ukhe wafuna ukunika izixhobo zakho zegaraji, iinxalenye zemoto, okanye i-console yakho yokudlala imbonakalo entsha neyohlukileyo? Ungajongi ngaphezulu kwefilimu ye-hydro dipping! I-Hydro dipping, ekwabizwa ngokuba kushicilelo lokugqithiselwa kwamanzi, yindlela yokusebenzisa uyilo oluprintiweyo kwizinto ezinomacala amathathu. Ingasetyenziswa kwizinto ezahlukeneyo ezifana neplastiki, isinyithi, iinkuni, iglasi, kunye nokunye, kuyenza ibe yindlela eguquguqukayo nenomtsalane wamehlo wokuguqula
... 
o lwesiko kunye neepateni kwiindawo zemoto kunye nezixhobo ezinje ngeerimu, i-interior trim, kunye nesigqubuthelo senjini. Ukukwazi ukwenza ukugqiba okukhethekileyo kunye nokwenziwe umntu kukwenza ukuba kube lukhetho oludumileyo phakathi kwabathandi bemoto kunye nabathengi abaziingcali abafuna ukugqama phakathi kwesihlwele.
Ukongeza kwizicelo zeemoto, ifilimu ye-hydro dipping ikwasetyenziswa kwimveliso yempahla yabathengi kunye ne-elektroniki. Iimveliso ezinje ngee-consoles zokudlala, abalawuli,
...
Ukusuka kubathandi beemoto kunye nabavelisi ukuya kwii-hobbyists kunye nabahombisi, ifilimu ye-hydro dipping ifumene indawo yayo njengendlela edumileyo yokufezekisa ukugqitywa kwesiko kunye nokuzisa ubuchule kwizinto zemihla ngemihla. Ngobuchule obufanelekileyo kunye nengqalelo kwiinkcukacha, ifilimu ye-hydro dipping inokuguqula umphezulu ngesitayile kwaye inike imbonakalo ehlala ihleli kwaye inefuthe.
